The paper compares blockchains and distributed databases as transactional systems, which suggests that it could belong to the databases (cs.DB) or distributed systems (cs.DC, cs.DS) categories. The focus on security and performance also suggests that it could belong to the cryptography and security (cs.CR) or software engineering (cs.SE) categories.
